# Poperechnoye, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Poperechnoye (; , Tailuud) is a rural locality (a selo) in Yeravninsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population is 383, as of 2010. There are 15 streets.
Geography
Poperechnoye is located 60&nbsp;km southwest of Sosnovo-Ozerskoye (the district's administrative centre) by road. Mozhayka is the nearest rural locality.
